Detailed Description

GENERATED CLASS.

Represents the <gates> XML element in memory. DTD declaration:

 <!ELEMENT gates (gate*)>
 <!ATTLIST gates
      banner-comment      CDATA     IMPLIED
      right-comment       CDATA     "&#10;" >
